{"_id":"GjEUKFtBtrxnAiu8","name":"Tier 2 Melee Critical Hits (Levels 5-8)","description":"Critical hit effects for melee attacks at Tier 2 (Levels 5-8). Effects are more impactful for competent adventurers.","img":"icons/skills/melee/strike-sword-slashing-red.webp","formula":"1d100","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"results":[{"_id":"Otip8OvJ4DjKTh77","type":0,"text":"Nothing Special - Your critical strike deals damage as normal, but no additional effect occurs.","img":"icons/svg/d20-highlight.svg","weight":18,"range":[1,18],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"none"}}},{"_id":"cFFxZ4ZGOXUew64v","type":0,"text":"Ringing Skull - Your blow rings against the target's skull and leaves their ears ringing. They are deafened until they receive healing.","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","weight":8,"range":[19,26],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"deafened","duration":-1}}},{"_id":"YItxilKTyWRQNnkp","type":0,"text":"Concentration Breaker - Your powerful hit rattles the target's focus. They have disadvantage on concentration saves until the end of their next turn.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":7,"range":[27,33],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"concentration","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Concentration Breaker","duration":0}}},{"_id":"sRNyxzSTd74g9A03","type":0,"text":"Rattling Strike - The blow shakes your foe's nerve. They have disadvantage on their next saving throw.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":7,"range":[34,40],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"save.all","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Rattled","duration":0}}},{"_id":"PpJQfn2si9IHF3BU","type":0,"text":"Armor Breach - Your attack finds a seam and warps their protection. They take -2 AC until the armor is repaired.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":6,"range":[41,46],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"penalty","penaltyType":"ac","penaltyValue":-2,"duration":-1}}},{"_id":"EawPkrQ7JyqLC7ES","type":0,"text":"Crippled Arm - Your strike mangles the target's weapon arm. They take -2 to attack rolls until they receive healing.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":6,"range":[47,52],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"penalty","penaltyType":"attack","penaltyValue":-2,"duration":-1}}},{"_id":"qs94cUiMaeb0o6Bj","type":0,"text":"Disorienting Hit - Your devastating strike leaves your target dazed. They have disadvantage on all attacks until the end of their next turn.","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","weight":6,"range":[53,58],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Disoriented","duration":1}}},{"_id":"WvXK0NfIBoHPozUL","type":0,"text":"Staggering Blow - Your powerful strike sends the target reeling. They are knocked prone.","img":"icons/svg/falling.svg","weight":5,"range":[59,63],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"prone","duration":0}}},{"_id":"Gld1A0uB3Khv3sFl","type":0,"text":"Weapon Lodged - Your weapon bites deep and tears loose, dealing 1d6 extra damage.","img":"icons/svg/sword.svg","weight":5,"range":[64,68],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"1d6","damageType":"weapon"}}},{"_id":"XHlDEbBRoYYLhQ7J","type":0,"text":"Deep Wound - Your strike opens a grievous wound. The target takes an extra weapon die of damage.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":5,"range":[69,73],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"1W","damageType":"weapon"}}},{"_id":"2TiImk0qpnu4nSiq","type":0,"text":"Driving Slam - You drive your full weight into the blow. The target must succeed on a DC 13 Strength save or be knocked prone.","img":"icons/svg/falling.svg","weight":5,"range":[74,78],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":13,"saveAbility":"str","effectCondition":"prone","duration":0}}},{"_id":"LK01zUCkPGnnTBT8","type":0,"text":"Bleeding Wound - Your strike opens a wound that will not close. The target takes 1d4 damage at the start of each of its turns until it receives magical healing or an ally uses an action to make a DC 10 Medicine check to stop the bleeding.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":4,"range":[79,82],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"1d4","damageType":"weapon","duration":-1}}},{"_id":"QSmgGAN7Fua1Dx1U","type":0,"text":"Hamstrung - Your blade slices across the back of the target's leg. They are restrained until the end of their next turn.","img":"icons/svg/net.svg","weight":4,"range":[83,86],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"restrained","duration":1}}},{"_id":"D0H5qMNVqhlPTTaS","type":0,"text":"Blood in the Eyes - Your blow splashes blood across the target's face. They are blinded until the end of their next turn.","img":"icons/svg/blind.svg","weight":4,"range":[87,90],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"blinded","duration":0}}},{"_id":"26udyxNAQSU6SGfW","type":0,"text":"Exposed Defenses - Your attack reveals the target's weaknesses. Attacks against them have advantage until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/target.svg","weight":3,"range":[91,93],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"advantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","advantageTarget":"grants","effectName":"Exposed Defenses","duration":1}}},{"_id":"fypFJZG0OOjQZgGc","type":0,"text":"Terrorizing Blow - Your brutal strike breaks the target's nerve. They must succeed on a DC 13 Wisdom save or be frightened of you until the end of their next turn.","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","weight":3,"range":[94,96],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":13,"saveAbility":"wis","effectCondition":"frightened","duration":1}}},{"_id":"ZS5IpTT8j9u0hQ6v","type":0,"text":"Bone-Deep Gash - Your blade carves a deep slashing wound. The target takes 2d6 slashing damage.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":2,"range":[97,98],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"2d6","damageType":"slashing"}}},{"_id":"PbVAxEjwGwEoiuDy","type":0,"text":"Ribcracker - Your blow caves in the target's ribs and drives the wind from them. They must succeed on a DC 13 Constitution save or be stunned until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","weight":2,"range":[99,100],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":13,"saveAbility":"con","effectCondition":"stunned","duration":1}}}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"tier":2,"attackType":"melee","resultType":"crit"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"4.0.0","coreVersion":"13.0","createdTime":1783951849385,"modifiedTime":1783951849385,"lastModifiedBy":"build-script"}}
{"_id":"QvjrHk93jjPHQnru","name":"Tier 2 Melee Fumbles (Levels 5-8)","description":"Fumble effects for melee attacks at Tier 2 (Levels 5-8). Effects are more impactful for competent adventurers.","img":"icons/skills/melee/strike-sword-slashing-red.webp","formula":"1d100","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"results":[{"_id":"UzSKzTfGn94lIXSg","type":0,"text":"Nothing Special - You stumble but recover with no additional penalty.","img":"icons/svg/d20-grey.svg","weight":18,"range":[1,18],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"none"}}},{"_id":"rUsm0VM9yP1w2GsE","type":0,"text":"Jarred Wrist - You jar your wrist on the botched swing, taking a -2 penalty to attack rolls until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":8,"range":[19,26],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"penalty","penaltyType":"attack","penaltyValue":-2,"duration":1}}},{"_id":"YB3IKhNNoSRgt4Mr","type":0,"text":"Off Your Feet - You lurch off balance and have disadvantage on your next saving throw.","img":"icons/svg/falling.svg","weight":7,"range":[27,33],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"save.all","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Off Your Feet","duration":0}}},{"_id":"AUvxCuna1d0su4n4","type":0,"text":"Lost Grip - Your weapon twists in your hand. You have disadvantage on your next melee weapon attack.","img":"icons/svg/sword.svg","weight":7,"range":[34,40],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"attack.mwak","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Lost Grip","duration":0}}},{"_id":"YN7oBn5gUiq3rNCK","type":0,"text":"Dropped Guard - You drop your guard, taking a -2 penalty to your AC until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":6,"range":[41,46],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"penalty","penaltyType":"ac","penaltyValue":-2,"duration":1}}},{"_id":"gJJiovOLZZlFa4QV","type":0,"text":"Ears Ringing - Your own clumsy blow rings your helm like a bell. You are deafened until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","weight":6,"range":[47,52],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"deafened","duration":1}}},{"_id":"qo69DHejl2eAnGfI","type":0,"text":"Telegraphed Attack - Your target reads your movements. It has advantage on its next attack against you.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":6,"range":[53,58],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"advantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","advantageTarget":"grants","effectName":"Telegraphed","duration":0}}},{"_id":"LBeP6fAjHzp7apGd","type":0,"text":"Muscle Tear - You badly strain a muscle. Take 1d6 bludgeoning damage.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":5,"range":[59,63],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"1d6","damageType":"bludgeoning"}}},{"_id":"Ph5BhKqwza1FoqBi","type":0,"text":"Shaken Confidence - Your failure rattles you. You have disadvantage on attack rolls until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":5,"range":[64,68],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Shaken Confidence","duration":1}}},{"_id":"Pt9yMUkfqPxWWJ51","type":0,"text":"Massive Opening - Your clumsy attack leaves you exposed. Attacks against you have advantage until the start of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":5,"range":[69,73],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"advantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","advantageTarget":"grants","effectName":"Massive Opening","duration":1}}},{"_id":"G50eY1QjEVv8T9Tt","type":0,"text":"Sprawled - Your wild swing throws you off balance and you fall prone.","img":"icons/svg/falling.svg","weight":5,"range":[74,78],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"prone","duration":0}}},{"_id":"vInLaPJHVgKtvQCF","type":0,"text":"Cut Yourself - The blade bites you on the backswing. You take one weapon die of damage to yourself.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":4,"range":[79,82],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"1W","damageType":"weapon"}}},{"_id":"8Bdln9jmn54v4QMr","type":0,"text":"Rattled - Your fumble rattles your nerve. You are frightened until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","weight":4,"range":[83,86],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"frightened","duration":1}}},{"_id":"B3Ag6evXh2LZtUCR","type":0,"text":"Weapon Flung - Your weapon flies from your grasp, landing well out of reach.","img":"icons/svg/sword.svg","weight":4,"range":[87,90],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disarm"}}},{"_id":"pgT28NkmHDmHyEgr","type":0,"text":"Grappling Straps - You tangle in your own straps and gear. You are grappled until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/net.svg","weight":3,"range":[91,93],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"grappled","duration":1}}},{"_id":"aNl1GMBmjtLlNoIl","type":0,"text":"Deep Self-Wound - Your weapon rebounds and gashes you deeply. Take 2d6 damage.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":3,"range":[94,96],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"2d6","damageType":"weapon"}}},{"_id":"DnGKbMcI5gLedNiE","type":0,"text":"Wild Swing - Your uncontrolled swing hits your nearest ally. Roll an attack against that ally's AC; on a hit, deal weapon damage.","img":"icons/svg/combat.svg","weight":2,"range":[97,98],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"attackAlly"}}},{"_id":"Tjduqz3jMgNaM98T","type":0,"text":"Devastating Rebound - Your weapon whips back at you. Make a DC 13 Constitution saving throw or take 2d6 damage and fall prone.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":2,"range":[99,100],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":13,"saveAbility":"con","effectCondition":"prone","damageFormula":"2d6","damageType":"weapon"}}}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"tier":2,"attackType":"melee","resultType":"fumble"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"4.0.0","coreVersion":"13.0","createdTime":1783951849385,"modifiedTime":1783951849385,"lastModifiedBy":"build-script"}}
{"_id":"5N3Qwh1t8n10lDG8","name":"Tier 2 Ranged Critical Hits (Levels 5-8)","description":"Critical hit effects for ranged attacks at Tier 2 (Levels 5-8). Effects are more impactful for competent adventurers.","img":"icons/weapons/bows/longbow-recurve-brown.webp","formula":"1d100","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"results":[{"_id":"EsgsIdVEs401ZkOC","type":0,"text":"Nothing Special - Your critical strike deals damage as normal, but no additional effect occurs.","img":"icons/svg/d20-highlight.svg","weight":18,"range":[1,18],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"none"}}},{"_id":"voBTMAqijI75TlId","type":0,"text":"Muffled Ears - The shot clips the side of the target's head, leaving them deafened until the wound is treated.","img":"icons/svg/silenced.svg","weight":8,"range":[19,26],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"deafened","duration":-1}}},{"_id":"tYENnBJdY68KPK2q","type":0,"text":"Staggering Shot - Your shot rocks the target, giving them disadvantage on their next attack roll.","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","weight":7,"range":[27,33],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","effectName":"Staggered","duration":0}}},{"_id":"8Z8LazpKWbzrfT6N","type":0,"text":"Disrupting Shot - Your shot breaks the target's concentration, giving them disadvantage on their next saving throw.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":7,"range":[34,40],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"save.all","effectName":"Disrupted","duration":0}}},{"_id":"rvLJms7LdXQvAWd0","type":0,"text":"Severed Tendon - Your shot severs a tendon in the target's arm, giving them -2 to attack rolls until they receive healing.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":6,"range":[41,46],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"penalty","penaltyType":"attack","penaltyValue":-2,"duration":-1}}},{"_id":"RROpCFVsy6L1v3KI","type":0,"text":"Armor Piercing - Your shot wedges into a gap in the plate, imposing -2 AC until the target readjusts their armor.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":6,"range":[47,52],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"penalty","penaltyType":"ac","penaltyValue":-2,"duration":-1}}},{"_id":"JdLPCV8IfkZwXmwi","type":0,"text":"Suppressing Shot - A burst of covering fire breaks the target's nerve, giving them disadvantage on attack rolls until the end of their next turn.","img":"icons/svg/net.svg","weight":6,"range":[53,58],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Suppressed","duration":1}}},{"_id":"4ZW3gSmn9uQu5QQp","type":0,"text":"Exposed Target - Your shot reveals the target's weakness, granting advantage on attacks against them until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/target.svg","weight":5,"range":[59,63],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"advantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","advantageTarget":"grants","effectName":"Exposed Target","duration":1}}},{"_id":"EktV0HL7iNTD3s23","type":0,"text":"Through and Through - Your projectile passes clean through, dealing an extra weapon die of damage.","img":"icons/svg/thrust.svg","weight":5,"range":[64,68],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"1W","damageType":"weapon"}}},{"_id":"ERHnxAtU6lKsMi1A","type":0,"text":"Knock Down - The force of your shot sweeps the target off their feet, knocking them prone.","img":"icons/svg/falling.svg","weight":5,"range":[69,73],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"prone","duration":0}}},{"_id":"Y2HNO7MnKUfbtxaC","type":0,"text":"Grit in the Eye - A spray of grit and blood catches the target across the eyes, leaving them blinded until the end of their next turn.","img":"icons/svg/blind.svg","weight":5,"range":[74,78],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"blinded","duration":0}}},{"_id":"37VlQeBxNLbVyn1a","type":0,"text":"Bleeder - The wound opens wide and bleeds freely, dealing an extra 2d6 piercing damage.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":4,"range":[79,82],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"2d6","damageType":"piercing"}}},{"_id":"AxWnK9uk63whVbVT","type":0,"text":"Kneecapped - Your shot strikes the target's knee, forcing a DC 13 Dexterity save or be knocked prone.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":4,"range":[83,86],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":13,"saveAbility":"dex","effectCondition":"prone"}}},{"_id":"yOUvLESvSshNcHP2","type":0,"text":"Nailed Down - The projectile nails a fold of the target to the ground, leaving them restrained until the end of their next turn.","img":"icons/svg/net.svg","weight":4,"range":[87,90],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"restrained","duration":1}}},{"_id":"KB75amrIjlJsllap","type":0,"text":"Sinking Terror - A shot to a vital spot fills the target with dread, forcing a DC 13 Wisdom save or be frightened of you.","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","weight":3,"range":[91,93],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":13,"saveAbility":"wis","effectCondition":"frightened"}}},{"_id":"cAdBOyjiLJThuFt5","type":0,"text":"Punctured Lung - Your shot punctures a lung, forcing a DC 13 Constitution save or be poisoned while the target struggles to breathe.","img":"icons/svg/poison.svg","weight":3,"range":[94,96],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":13,"saveAbility":"con","effectCondition":"poisoned"}}},{"_id":"Zc4DSQqzsfx847nY","type":0,"text":"Devastating Shot - Your perfectly placed shot deals an extra two weapon dice of damage.","img":"icons/svg/explosion.svg","weight":2,"range":[97,98],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"2W","damageType":"weapon"}}},{"_id":"8TqODt8IFgLks3Pj","type":0,"text":"Legendary Shot - A masterful shot lands with maximum weapon damage and leaves the target frightened of you for two rounds.","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","weight":2,"range":[99,100],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"frightened","duration":2}}}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"tier":2,"attackType":"ranged","resultType":"crit"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"4.0.0","coreVersion":"13.0","createdTime":1783951849386,"modifiedTime":1783951849386,"lastModifiedBy":"build-script"}}
{"_id":"FWd8rLXOgKI04rl6","name":"Tier 2 Ranged Fumbles (Levels 5-8)","description":"Fumble effects for ranged attacks at Tier 2 (Levels 5-8). Effects are more impactful for competent adventurers.","img":"icons/weapons/bows/longbow-recurve-brown.webp","formula":"1d100","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"results":[{"_id":"SkpMJt3xm4LM1viH","type":0,"text":"Nothing Special - Your shot goes wide but you recover with no additional penalty.","img":"icons/svg/d20-grey.svg","weight":18,"range":[1,18],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"none"}}},{"_id":"Ue8VVQG7opoG50i6","type":0,"text":"Watering Eyes - Your eyes water from the effort and you have disadvantage on your next ability check.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":8,"range":[19,26],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"ability.all","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Watering Eyes","duration":0}}},{"_id":"yPx6iEiNnVGTnJ1M","type":0,"text":"Flinch - You flinch at your own misfire and have disadvantage on your next saving throw.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":7,"range":[27,33],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"save.all","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Flinch","duration":0}}},{"_id":"yfaqFjAbm1gGOhmn","type":0,"text":"Snapped String - Your bowstring snaps taut awkwardly and you have disadvantage on ranged attacks until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":7,"range":[34,40],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"attack.rwak","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Snapped String","duration":1}}},{"_id":"TWJvIw3fe3bRYLGF","type":0,"text":"Fouled Aim - Your aim is thrown off and you have disadvantage on your next attack roll.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":6,"range":[41,46],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Fouled Aim","duration":0}}},{"_id":"333piBm5Y51qpOxo","type":0,"text":"Overdrawn - You overdraw and wrench your form, taking a -2 penalty to attack rolls until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":6,"range":[47,52],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"penalty","penaltyType":"attack","penaltyValue":-2,"duration":1}}},{"_id":"FByfKXSH1CbLNag8","type":0,"text":"Recoil Strain - The recoil wrenches your arm; take 1d6 bludgeoning damage.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":6,"range":[53,58],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"1d6","damageType":"bludgeoning"}}},{"_id":"kObd0F4t94h3gukm","type":0,"text":"Telegraphed Shot - You telegraph your shot and your target has advantage on its next saving throw against you.","img":"icons/svg/target.svg","weight":5,"range":[59,63],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"advantage","advantageScope":"save.all","advantageTarget":"grants","effectName":"Telegraphed Shot","duration":0}}},{"_id":"UnBRcTp889jKXodS","type":0,"text":"Caught Flat - You are caught flat-footed; attacks against you have advantage until the start of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/target.svg","weight":5,"range":[64,68],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"advantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","advantageTarget":"grants","effectName":"Caught Flat","duration":1}}},{"_id":"FM85p6hyUk6Pwn95","type":0,"text":"Jammed Solid - Your weapon jams solid and you have disadvantage on attack rolls until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":5,"range":[69,73],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Jammed Solid","duration":1}}},{"_id":"ZOgSHOzvB9TMWbTM","type":0,"text":"Exposed Flank - Your stance falls apart, leaving a -2 penalty to your AC until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":5,"range":[74,78],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"penalty","penaltyType":"ac","penaltyValue":-2,"duration":1}}},{"_id":"FMdSFQ33KlUqhgJJ","type":0,"text":"Dropped Weapon - Your ranged weapon flies from your hands, landing 20 feet away.","img":"icons/svg/net.svg","weight":4,"range":[79,82],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disarm"}}},{"_id":"piHJVegdywEuYNlX","type":0,"text":"Off-Balance - You lose your footing; make a DC 13 Dexterity saving throw or fall prone.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":4,"range":[83,86],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":13,"saveAbility":"dex","effectCondition":"prone","duration":-1}}},{"_id":"zvKhvTkG20NmixEF","type":0,"text":"Winded - The strain knocks the wind from you; make a DC 13 Constitution saving throw or take 1d8 bludgeoning damage.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":4,"range":[87,90],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":13,"saveAbility":"con","damageFormula":"1d8","damageType":"bludgeoning"}}},{"_id":"XNszCHdlQYirfytj","type":0,"text":"Blinded - Your snapped string lashes across your eyes; you are blinded until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/paralysis.svg","weight":3,"range":[91,93],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"blinded","duration":1}}},{"_id":"C99IybJ3ouhIeUsx","type":0,"text":"Self-Injury - The weapon rebounds and injures you; take 2d6 bludgeoning damage.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":3,"range":[94,96],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"2d6","damageType":"bludgeoning"}}},{"_id":"hsDgJkQvrcjs8Qxh","type":0,"text":"Tangled Sling - Your sling or strap wraps around you; you are restrained until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/net.svg","weight":2,"range":[97,98],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"restrained","duration":1}}},{"_id":"U8O4QQ5qCQa1EhDr","type":0,"text":"Wild Ricochet - Your shot ricochets wildly toward the nearest ally; roll an attack against their AC.","img":"icons/svg/combat.svg","weight":2,"range":[99,100],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"attackAlly"}}}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"tier":2,"attackType":"ranged","resultType":"fumble"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"4.0.0","coreVersion":"13.0","createdTime":1783951849386,"modifiedTime":1783951849386,"lastModifiedBy":"build-script"}}
{"_id":"T3Nh67rOMNTqzVSM","name":"Tier 2 Spell Critical Hits (Levels 5-8)","description":"Critical hit effects for spell attacks at Tier 2 (Levels 5-8). Effects are more impactful for competent adventurers.","img":"icons/magic/fire/projectile-fireball-smoke-strong-orange.webp","formula":"1d100","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"results":[{"_id":"jB6XnaJMcFvSppbD","type":0,"text":"Nothing Special - Your critical spell deals damage as normal, but no additional effect occurs.","img":"icons/svg/d20-highlight.svg","weight":18,"range":[1,18],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"none"}}},{"_id":"8aZIRSKzZ1VIN2HY","type":0,"text":"Ringing Aura - A piercing arcane tone rings in the target's ears, leaving them deafened.","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","weight":8,"range":[19,26],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"deafened","duration":-1}}},{"_id":"PJ6ptkA43AT5tuVJ","type":0,"text":"Concentration Shatter - Your spell disrupts focus. If concentrating, they have disadvantage on the save with a -5 penalty.","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","weight":7,"range":[27,33],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"concentration","effectName":"Concentration Shatter","duration":0}}},{"_id":"Ws0ErI90bb7MsXfd","type":0,"text":"Mind Fog - Your spell clouds the target's mind. They have disadvantage on their next saving throw.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":7,"range":[34,40],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"save.all","effectName":"Mind Fog","duration":0}}},{"_id":"P2GtwCpI1VJn95VQ","type":0,"text":"Sluggish Mind - The target's thoughts turn to sludge, giving them disadvantage on saving throws until the end of their next turn.","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","weight":6,"range":[41,46],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"save.all","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Sluggish Mind","duration":1}}},{"_id":"A2vL1ysOfFLiaSmT","type":0,"text":"Magic Disruption - Your spell disrupts their magical abilities. Target has disadvantage on spell attacks for 2 rounds.","img":"icons/svg/silenced.svg","weight":6,"range":[47,52],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":["attack.msak","attack.rsak"],"effectName":"Magic Disruption","duration":2}}},{"_id":"DJg2WRBaeFa0XP5O","type":0,"text":"Hex of Frailty - A hex of frailty erodes the target's defenses, giving them a -2 penalty to AC until removed.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":6,"range":[53,58],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"penalty","penaltyType":"ac","penaltyValue":-2,"duration":-1}}},{"_id":"vGDc7do1ZJiMlXmk","type":0,"text":"Arcane Burn - Magical energy sears the target. They take extra force damage equal to the spell's damage die at the start of their next turn.","img":"icons/magic/fire/flame-burning-yellow-orange.webp","weight":5,"range":[59,63],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"1S","damageType":"force"}}},{"_id":"PTIn4iF0nLovmaFn","type":0,"text":"Elemental Surge - Your spell's element flares dramatically. Add extra damage equal to two of the spell's damage dice, of the spell's type.","img":"icons/svg/explosion.svg","weight":5,"range":[64,68],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"2S","damageType":"spell"}}},{"_id":"iv2hZnBtpHJy0Iks","type":0,"text":"Mana Burn - Raw magic ignites the target's own reserves, dealing 2d6 force damage.","img":"icons/svg/explosion.svg","weight":5,"range":[69,73],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"2d6","damageType":"force"}}},{"_id":"VeIecduFCFCKcgnJ","type":0,"text":"Arcane Amplification - Your magical power surges! Deal additional force damage equal to two of the spell's damage dice.","img":"icons/svg/explosion.svg","weight":5,"range":[74,78],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"2S","damageType":"force"}}},{"_id":"nX1z8sOPbelA59Ft","type":0,"text":"Withering Curse - A withering hex corrodes the target from within; they must succeed on a DC 13 Constitution save or be poisoned.","img":"icons/svg/poison.svg","weight":4,"range":[79,82],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":13,"saveAbility":"con","effectCondition":"poisoned"}}},{"_id":"OsAEKxFnP8HweKj9","type":0,"text":"Numbing Frost - Creeping frost locks the target's limbs; they must succeed on a DC 13 Strength save or be restrained.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":4,"range":[83,86],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":13,"saveAbility":"str","effectCondition":"restrained"}}},{"_id":"W6YC681SLaVaXchL","type":0,"text":"Mind Spike - A lance of psychic force stabs the target's mind; they must succeed on a DC 13 Wisdom save or be frightened of you.","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","weight":4,"range":[87,90],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":13,"saveAbility":"wis","effectCondition":"frightened"}}},{"_id":"wvbtPZ4JXFMBcE7U","type":0,"text":"Dazzling Display - Your spell creates a blinding flash. The target is blinded until the end of their next turn.","img":"icons/svg/blind.svg","weight":3,"range":[91,93],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"blinded","duration":1}}},{"_id":"vhestR2EH0FbpURA","type":0,"text":"Powerful Knockback - The force of your spell sends the target flying. They are pushed 15 feet and fall prone.","img":"icons/svg/thrust.svg","weight":3,"range":[94,96],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"prone","duration":0}}},{"_id":"Ta5TYwh7ItK0Q1ot","type":0,"text":"Arcane Vulnerability - Your magic leaves the target exposed. Attacks against them have advantage until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/target.svg","weight":2,"range":[97,98],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"advantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","advantageTarget":"grants","effectName":"Arcane Vulnerability","duration":1}}},{"_id":"ppmDrYbFzxnBYKo4","type":0,"text":"Stunning Spell - The magical energy overwhelms the target. They are stunned until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","weight":2,"range":[99,100],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"stunned","duration":1}}}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"tier":2,"attackType":"spell","resultType":"crit"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"4.0.0","coreVersion":"13.0","createdTime":1783951849386,"modifiedTime":1783951849386,"lastModifiedBy":"build-script"}}
{"_id":"ZEaUk4ZPjVpAkLIY","name":"Tier 2 Spell Fumbles (Levels 5-8)","description":"Fumble effects for spell attacks at Tier 2 (Levels 5-8). Effects are more impactful for competent adventurers.","img":"icons/magic/fire/projectile-fireball-smoke-strong-orange.webp","formula":"1d100","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"results":[{"_id":"KitCDZMRESeA8VB2","type":0,"text":"Nothing Special - Your spell fizzles harmlessly with no additional penalty.","img":"icons/svg/d20-grey.svg","weight":18,"range":[1,18],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"none"}}},{"_id":"2rYTqYlj2rAEpvU6","type":0,"text":"Grounded Magic - Your spell earths itself through your body. You have disadvantage on attack rolls until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":8,"range":[19,26],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Grounded Magic","duration":1}}},{"_id":"nuXUVIh6ysEoB3u8","type":0,"text":"Spell Recoil - The spell lashes back as it leaves you. You have disadvantage on your next ranged spell attack.","img":"icons/svg/lightning.svg","weight":7,"range":[27,33],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"attack.rsak","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Spell Recoil","duration":0}}},{"_id":"6oAFKgqU1vvRs1jl","type":0,"text":"Arcane Hiccup - Your magic stutters and misfires. You have disadvantage on spell attacks until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":7,"range":[34,40],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":["attack.msak","attack.rsak"],"advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Arcane Hiccup","duration":1}}},{"_id":"o1RTjP0yjAHK2WVQ","type":0,"text":"Somatic Cramp - Your casting hand cramps violently. You have disadvantage on concentration checks until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","weight":6,"range":[41,46],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"concentration","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Somatic Cramp","duration":1}}},{"_id":"ciOFK1HntAYvstKq","type":0,"text":"Arcane Backlash - Raw magic rebounds into you. Take force damage equal to one of the spell's damage dice.","img":"icons/svg/explosion.svg","weight":6,"range":[47,52],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"1S","damageType":"force"}}},{"_id":"A9ayf822LwZSrgrZ","type":0,"text":"Component Combustion - Your material components ignite in your grip. Take 1d6 fire damage.","img":"icons/svg/fire.svg","weight":6,"range":[53,58],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"1d6","damageType":"fire"}}},{"_id":"B9Gk2CEdYiRmzmNm","type":0,"text":"Telegraphed Magic - Your fumbled casting tips your hand. Enemies have advantage on their next saving throw against your spells.","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","weight":5,"range":[59,63],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"advantage","advantageScope":"save.all","advantageTarget":"grants","effectName":"Telegraphed Magic","duration":0}}},{"_id":"4VaBhiXvoGLE19j3","type":0,"text":"Exposed Weave - Your botched weave leaves you unguarded. Attacks against you have advantage until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":5,"range":[64,68],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"advantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","advantageTarget":"grants","effectName":"Exposed Weave","duration":1}}},{"_id":"YDFfqjnSLfSJz68R","type":0,"text":"Warped Focus - The recoil throws off your aim. You take a -2 penalty to attack rolls until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":5,"range":[69,73],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"penalty","penaltyType":"attack","penaltyValue":-2,"duration":1}}},{"_id":"rx3pNRShCCkvr5rU","type":0,"text":"Shattered Wards - The backlash shreds your protective wards. You take a -2 penalty to AC until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":5,"range":[74,78],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"penalty","penaltyType":"ac","penaltyValue":-2,"duration":1}}},{"_id":"6Jo9bxyTnJW7cnRu","type":0,"text":"Backlash Sprawl - The detonation throws you off your feet. You are knocked prone.","img":"icons/svg/combat.svg","weight":4,"range":[79,82],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"prone","duration":0}}},{"_id":"kuGqKc9Z4IChxEa5","type":0,"text":"Deafening Boom - The spell erupts with a deafening crack. You are deafened.","img":"icons/svg/explosion.svg","weight":4,"range":[83,86],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"deafened","duration":-1}}},{"_id":"nyTR9aDOwWhvhdEX","type":0,"text":"Magical Backlash - The spell's energy rebounds painfully. Take 1d8 force damage.","img":"icons/svg/lightning.svg","weight":4,"range":[87,90],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"1d8","damageType":"force"}}},{"_id":"JZnebD4C39T6dfLY","type":0,"text":"Blinding Feedback - A blinding flash of misfired magic sears your eyes. You are blinded until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/blind.svg","weight":3,"range":[91,93],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"blinded","duration":0}}},{"_id":"8c1HQ48rhi9CeJMu","type":0,"text":"Catastrophic Rebound - Your spell collapses inward. Make a DC 13 Constitution saving throw or take 3d6 force damage and be knocked prone.","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","weight":3,"range":[94,96],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":13,"saveAbility":"con","damageFormula":"3d6","damageType":"force","effectCondition":"prone","failEffect":"Take force damage and be knocked prone"}}},{"_id":"4QuFlCAhqP3eSLb0","type":0,"text":"Wild Surge Jolt - Wild magic detonates through your body. Take 2d6 force damage.","img":"icons/svg/explosion.svg","weight":2,"range":[97,98],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"2d6","damageType":"force"}}},{"_id":"ybKlDEWdwAKa5kHs","type":0,"text":"Misfired Blast - Your spell veers wildly and misfires at the nearest ally. Make a spell attack against the nearest ally; on a hit, they take the spell's damage.","img":"icons/svg/combat.svg","weight":2,"range":[99,100],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"attackAlly"}}}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"tier":2,"attackType":"spell","resultType":"fumble"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"4.0.0","coreVersion":"13.0","createdTime":1783951849386,"modifiedTime":1783951849386,"lastModifiedBy":"build-script"}}